Present location: INSTITUT DE PAPYROLOGIE ET D'ÉGYPTOLOGIE, UNIVERSITÉ DE LILLE III [02/049] LILLE
Name: Documentary papyrus
Description: Documentary papyrus, the letter of a certain Demetrios (function and personal details not indicated) to Pankrates. Lines 2 and 3 are so mutilated that apart from naming a third person called Kallimachos (line 2), one can say nothing more.
